，好友耕司和學妹瑤查覺郁紀的異樣行為，分別採取行動，耕司跟蹤著郁紀，而瑤被沙耶利用青海的手機騙到郁紀家裏。耕司的跟蹤行動很快被發現，郁紀毫不留情把他推入冰冷的井裏；正當耕司打電話警告瑤時，卻聽到沙耶對瑤進行生物改造的聲音。回到家的郁紀，所看到的是他過去認識的瑤，當然事實上是被沙耶改造成怪物，精神也早已崩壞。耕司後來被涼子救起，涼子帶着他到奧涯教授的地下研究室，並告誡耕司往下追究會有危險，同時給他一把槍防身。此時耕司尚抱持一絲希望，再度打電話給郁紀，然而郁紀只是冷冷回答出青海可能被他吃下的事情。感到絕望的耕司來到郁紀家，發現那裏早已人去樓空，而冰箱內的屍體，被他認出是摯愛女友的手。在這絕望與瘋狂下，耕司決定<br />\n<br />\n以下2個結局："},{"pid":"e95415eb9cf9336db4e76020c241123bec77a253","tid":250852,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗起另一隻短篇RPG game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊一隻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RGOpeciH1iQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRGOpeciH1iQ&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=27e535ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RGOpeciH1iQ</a>"},{"pid":"c7993fa6017aedbcd66c2e8767474d8a8bb6cfe7","tid":250852,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗起另一隻短篇RPG game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊一隻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RGOpeciH1iQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRGOpeciH1iQ&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=27e535ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RGOpeciH1iQ</a></blockquote><br />\n我睇完簡介都覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"h